WEBVTT

00:06.474 --> 00:09.477
<i>MTV ♪</i>

00:09.610 --> 00:10.778
<i>Dwight Manfredi.</i>

00:10.911 --> 00:12.513
I got a rap sheet
in front of me.

00:12.646 --> 00:13.914
Goes back
to before the Beatles.

00:14.048 --> 00:15.349
He bought me a drink.
Nothing happened.

00:15.483 --> 00:16.984
I'm an ATF agent.

00:17.118 --> 00:18.486
Your picture
came through my office.

00:18.619 --> 00:20.188
Where to, boss?

00:20.321 --> 00:21.855
You should be in college.

00:21.989 --> 00:24.292
Dude a businessman.
I can learn a lot from.

00:24.425 --> 00:25.726
We'll be making money

00:25.859 --> 00:27.428
and the feds won't be able
to touch it.

00:27.561 --> 00:31.599
Need to see some ID.
This expired in 1998.

00:32.600 --> 00:33.667
That's the learners permit.

00:33.801 --> 00:35.436
There's other weed farms.

00:35.569 --> 00:37.271
You got to do better
on the price, Jimmy.

00:37.405 --> 00:40.874
1200 for the first ten units
and 750 after that.

00:41.008 --> 00:44.512
