I swallow this cracker.

00:45.213 --> 00:46.680
You drive a hard bargain.

00:46.814 --> 00:48.182
The thing with them.

00:49.350 --> 00:50.584
<i>You gotta make this right.</i>

00:50.718 --> 00:52.220
A hundred grand would do it.

00:52.353 --> 00:53.887
What does your family
think about you being here?

00:54.021 --> 00:55.389
- Your daughter.
- Tina.

00:57.458 --> 00:58.892
<i>It's him. The psycho.</i>

00:59.026 --> 01:01.729
Here's here to kill me.
I'm looking for a friend.

01:01.862 --> 01:03.531
I believe he's staying
at your hotel.

01:03.664 --> 01:06.434
Oh, Mr. Man.
From New York, right?

01:06.567 --> 01:08.602
That's him.

01:23.050 --> 01:24.618
<i>We have an officer shot.</i>

01:24.752 --> 01:26.154
<i>Condition currently stable.</i>

01:26.287 --> 01:28.322
<i>Ambulance en route
to Tulsa General.</i>

01:28.456 --> 01:31.159
<i>Suspect is barricaded.
Perimeter is secure.</i>

01:32.025 --> 01:33.661
<i>Copy that. 10-4.</i>

01:33.794 --> 01:35.463
Mr. Dumont,

01:35.596 --> 01:38.466
I'm giving you the opportunity
to surrender peacefully.

01:38.932 --> 01:41.902
If you comply, I guarantee
you will not be harmed.

01:42.035 --> 01:43.904
Get off my fucking property!

01:44.405 --> 01:46.507
This is not your property,
Mr. Dumont.

01:46.640 --> 01:47.708
Fuck you.

01:52.346 --> 01:53.481
Cue the cavalry.

02:05.193 --> 02:08.196
- Easy, Dumont!
- Keel!

02:10.398 --> 02:11.665
That you?

02:13.701 --> 02:15.369
Can you talk to him?

02:17.205 --> 02:19.207
Sounds to me like
his position is pretty clear.

02:19.307 --> 02:20.908
What the fuck
are you doing here

02:21.041 --> 02:22.310
if you're not going to help?

02:24.378 --> 02:26.214
Eh, witness.

02:26.914 --> 02:28.449
Get him the fuck out of here.

02:28.582 --> 02:29.983
They left you no choice Dumont.

02:35.956 --> 02:37.825
I'm letting my dogs out.

02:38.892 --> 02:40.228
Don't hurt them.

02:43.397 --> 02:44.665
They're good boys.

04:20.394 --> 04:24.598
