this old stuff?

05:17.150 --> 05:18.386
Love it.

05:18.486 --> 05:19.987
Make that next left
over there,

05:20.120 --> 05:21.689
don't forget
your hand signal either.

05:22.390 --> 05:23.691
No one does that anymore--

05:23.824 --> 05:25.759
