- You sure?

05:39.139 --> 05:40.508
I don't mind driving.

05:40.641 --> 05:42.410
Oh, you shouldn't mind.
I pay you enough.

05:43.444 --> 05:45.413
- About that, uh--
- Hey.

05:46.113 --> 05:47.581
