you don't have the balls

05:47.715 --> 05:49.417
to be asking me for a raise
this soon.

05:49.550 --> 05:51.419
All right, well,
let me ask you this.

05:52.720 --> 05:54.755
Where you see me
in the next five years?

05:54.888 --> 05:58.426
<i>♪ The expressway
is not the best way ♪</i>

05:58.559 --> 06:03.431
