- See me?

06:07.435 --> 06:09.136
Yeah. Five years.

06:09.637 --> 06:11.171
You realize
I'm a criminal, right?

06:11.304 --> 06:13.306
I got Google, man.
I know all about you.

06:13.441 --> 06:16.209
Where do you see you

06:16.343 --> 06:17.845
in five years?

06:17.978 --> 06:21.549
Like a position of power
or something, like a-- a capo?

06:21.682 --> 06:23.917
