- Oh, 'cause I'm not Italian?

06:24.051 --> 06:25.453
Ye-- that and beyond that.

06:25.453 --> 06:27.855
"Beyond that."
What? What? Why?

06:27.988 --> 06:29.256
Listen kid.

06:31.459 --> 06:33.360
You're not a boy scout,

06:33.494 --> 06:35.463
but you're not a bad guy either.

06:36.363 --> 06:37.465
You know what I'm saying?

06:38.766 --> 06:39.833
Hmm?

06:43.303 --> 06:45.038
Come on, you drive.

06:45.506 --> 06:47.007
You're a better driver anyway.

06:49.477 --> 06:51.545
<i>♪ Guess who's back
in the motherfucking house ♪</i>

06:51.679 --> 06:53.481
<i>With a big fat joint ♪</i>

06:53.581 --> 06:55.215
<i>♪ Girls get close,
rub me in my ointment ♪</i>

06:55.348 --> 06:57.485
<i>♪ So many chicks,
gotta make an appointment ♪</i>

06:57.618 --> 06:59.720
