broke up with boyfriend ♪</i>

07:03.290 --> 07:04.892
What's this,
a cut-rate Woodstock?

07:05.025 --> 07:08.095
- What's Woodstock?
-"What's Woodstock?" Jesus.

07:08.228 --> 07:10.030
Will you
shut the fuck up?

07:10.163 --> 07:12.265
